item.dc:creator: @pk3r_john pk3r john
item.description:
@pk3r_john wrote:

[quote=“Epic Ancient, post:2, topic:300524”]By using this magical little tool we can call, for now, a “Magic Bar.”
This “Magic Bar” lets you look allllllll over the forums for a problem, code, or something else you would want.
The correct term for this “Magic Bar” would be known as the “Search Bar”.
You might find that it can be, more often than not, simple to use!
Also, if you find using it was helpful in some way, or not, tell OTHER people about it, too!

–Lulz. Look in client.java.[/quote]

What a retarded post. Help the damn guy, search bar doesn’t work most of the time. (At least for me)

It’s in your client class, search for the one you have right now and just change it.
